00:00:04.990 --> 00:00:09.709
Put away your pots and pans, because you'll
only need one skillet to cook these five healthy

00:00:09.709 --> 00:00:16.840
dinners.

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:18.570
You'll need these items in your grocery bag.

00:00:18.570 --> 00:00:22.070
We'll give you the full shopping list at the
end of the video.

00:00:22.070 --> 00:00:27.859
Also, make sure you have these pantry staples
before you shop.

00:00:27.859 --> 00:00:33.390
On Monday, convenient frozen shredded hash
browns, zucchini and chickpeas make a crispy

00:00:33.390 --> 00:00:36.640
base for meatless Chickpea &amp; Potato Hash.

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:45.360
You'll also need ginger, baby spinach, onion,
curry powder and eggs.

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:49.640
On Tuesday, you'll make tilapia with a quick
tomato-olive pan sauce.

00:00:49.640 --> 00:00:55.909
Besides tilapia, you'll need grape tomatoes,
dry white wine, garlic and your favorite olive

00:00:55.909 --> 00:01:00.250
tapenade.

00:01:00.250 --> 00:01:05.260
On Wednesday, chicken drumsticks simmer in
your skillet with lots of garlic in a simple

00:01:05.260 --> 00:01:07.300
white-wine mustard sauce.

00:01:07.300 --> 00:01:13.429
You'll need garlic, chicken drumsticks, white
wine, reduced-sodium chicken broth and chives

00:01:13.429 --> 00:01:17.490
to make this French bistro-worthy meal at
home.

00:01:17.490 --> 00:01:23.579
On Thursday, a fast Bell Pepper &amp; Beef Curry
gets lots of color and fiber from green beans,

00:01:23.579 --> 00:01:25.560
red bell peppers and mango.

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:33.829
This meal also includes beef sirloin, canned
light coconut milk, red curry paste and a

00:01:33.829 --> 00:01:36.439
lime.

00:01:36.439 --> 00:01:42.049
On Friday, gnocchi cooks right in the skillet,
along with shrimp, shallot, asparagus and

00:01:42.049 --> 00:01:46.249
Parmesan cheese, for a saucy one-pan pasta
dish.

00:01:46.249 --> 00:01:50.090
You'll also need reduced-sodium chicken broth
and a lemon.

00:01:50.090 --> 00:02:06.979
With only one pan to clean, this easy dinner
is the perfect way to end a long week.

00:02:06.979 --> 00:02:13.250
Get these five healthy recipes plus a shopping
list for the week at eatingwell.com/one bag.

